Real-world SOP summary (1-page style)
Aise likh sakte ho change ticket / SOP me:

Pre-steps
Instance details note karo (ID, Name, IP, OS)
AMI backup banao
Login
SSH using key pair

Pre checks
whoami, hostname -f
cat /etc/os-release
uname -r
df -h, free -h, uptime

Repo & updates
yum repolist
yum check-update

Apply patches
Security only: yum update --security -y
Full: yum update -y

Check reboot requirement
Install utils: yum install -y yum-utils
needs-restarting -r
Reboot
reboot

Post checks
uname -r
systemctl status <services>

App/URL test
Logs & cleanup
cat /var/log/yum.log
yum clean all
